类 Launch

  • java.lang.Object
    • Launch
  • public class Launch
extends java.lang.Object
    This class intends to launch the whole Application with the simple interface in command line model to users.
    版本:
    1.0
    作者:
    Zhiwei Cao, Jiahe Jin, Minghao Zhou, Liangqi Cai, Tianwei Bao, Seungjun Chong, Yunzhao Liu

      • Launch

        public Launch()
       throws java.io.IOException

      • viewAll

        public void viewAll​(java.lang.String command)
        This method intends to print out the all Pokemon within the PokemonTable. By entering the second command with [a], like [ax] where the [x] is the second command, users can get the specific values of pokemon with its name. When users just enter the [a], all Pokemon's name will be output. When users enter [a][a], all Pokemon's name with all of other attributes will be output together.
        参数:
        command - the command being assigned from users

      • check

        public void check​(java.lang.String name)
        This method intends to get all specific attributes (information) of the Pokemon by searching its name.
        参数:
        name - the name of Pokemon searched

      • document

        public boolean document()
        This method intends to help users add their own Pokemon into the PokemonTable
        返回:
        true if the Pokemon is successfully added, false if the Pokemon is not added
